,"Emerging AI Technologies","Emerging technologies and research directions in AI","_ai/emerging.md",{"type":183,"children":184,"toc":349},"root",[185,194,201,207,230,236,241,268,274,279,290,296,301,320,325,330],{"type":186,"tag":187,"props":188,"children":190},"element","h1",{"id":189},"新兴技术-emerging-technologies",[191],{"type":192,"value":193},"text","新兴技术 (Emerging Technologies)",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":196,"children":198},"h2",{"id":197},"moe稀疏激活的参数扩展",[199],{"type":192,"value":200},"MoE：稀疏激活的参数扩展",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":203,"children":204},"p",{},[205],{"type":192,"value":206},"混合专家模型（MoE）将前馈层替换为多个\"专家\"网络，通过门控网络动态选择激活的专家。DeepSeek-V3 是 MoE 标杆，拥有 671B 总参数但每次只激活 37B，在保持推理成本不变的情况下显著扩展模型容量。2025 年 MoE 成为大模型标配，Mixtral、Qwen3、Gemini 1.5 Pro 均采用此架构。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":208,"children":209},{},[210,212,221,223],{"type":192,"value":211},"见：",{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":214,"children":218},"a",{"href":215,"rel":216},"https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.19437",[217],"nofollow",[219],{"type":192,"value":220},"DeepSeek-V3 技术报告",{"type":192,"value":222}," | ",{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":224,"children":227},{"href":225,"rel":226},"https://cameronrwolfe.substack.com/p/moe-llms",[217],[228],{"type":192,"value":229},"MoE LLMs 详解",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":231,"children":233},{"id":232},"jepa非生成式世界模型",[234],{"type":192,"value":235},"JEPA：非生成式世界模型",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":237,"children":238},{},[239],{"type":192,"value":240},"JEPA（Joint Embedding Predictive Architecture）是杨立昆（Yann LeCun）提出的非生成式自监督学习架构。不同于 LLM 在像素/token 空间预测，JEPA 在抽象表示空间进行预测，关注高层语义而非低层细节。2025 年 Meta 发布 V-JEPA 2，结合互联网视频与机器人轨迹数据，在视觉理解上达到 SOTA。VL-JEPA 进一步拓展到视觉-语言多模态领域。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":242,"children":243},{},[244,245,252,253,260,261],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":246,"children":249},{"href":247,"rel":248},"https://ai.meta.com/research/vjepa/",[217],[250],{"type":192,"value":251},"V-JEPA 2 官方发布",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":254,"children":257},{"href":255,"rel":256},"https://rohitbandaru.github.io/blog/JEPA-Deep-Dive/",[217],[258],{"type":192,"value":259},"JEPA 深度解析",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":262,"children":265},{"href":263,"rel":264},"https://medium.com/@harshit.sinha0910/what-vl-jepa-could-revolutionize-in-multimodal-intelligence-a1c2105dc62e",[217],[266],{"type":192,"value":267},"VL-JEPA 多模态突破",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":269,"children":271},{"id":270},"空间智能李飞飞的-ai-愿景",[272],{"type":192,"value":273},"空间智能：李飞飞的 AI 愿景",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":275,"children":276},{},[277],{"type":192,"value":278},"李飞飞认为当前 LLM 只是\"系统一\"的快速思考，真正的 AI 需要具备\"空间智能\"——理解三维世界的几何、物理和语义关系。世界模型需要具备生成性（创造物理一致的世界）、多模态（融合视觉、语言、空间）、交互性（支持探索和导航）三大特征。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":280,"children":281},{},[282,283],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":284,"children":287},{"href":285,"rel":286},"https://www.mittrchina.com/news/detail/15468",[217],[288],{"type":192,"value":289},"李飞飞空间智能宣言",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":291,"children":293},{"id":292},"投机解码推理加速新范式",[294],{"type":192,"value":295},"投机解码：推理加速新范式",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":297,"children":298},{},[299],{"type":192,"value":300},"投机解码用小模型（draft）快速生成候选 token，大模型（target）并行验证，理想情况下可加速 2-3 倍。2025 年该技术真正成熟，华为诺亚提出 ViSpec 方法首次实现多模态大模型高效投机推理，加速比达 3.2 倍。与 MoE 结合有协同效应。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":302,"children":303},{},[304,305,312,313],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":306,"children":309},{"href":307,"rel":308},"https://developer.nvidia.cn/blog/an-introduction-to-speculative-decoding-for-reducing-latency-in-ai-inference/",[217],[310],{"type":192,"value":311},"NVIDIA 投机解码介绍",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":314,"children":317},{"href":315,"rel":316},"https://hub.baai.ac.cn/view/49232",[217],[318],{"type":192,"value":319},"ViSpec NeurIPS 2025",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":321,"children":323},{"id":322},"模型合并与长上下文",[324],{"type":192,"value":322},{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":326,"children":327},{},[328],{"type":192,"value":329},"模型合并通过权重空间插值将多个微调模型融合，Task Arithmetic、TIES-Merging、Model Soups 等技术实现零训练集成。长上下文技术包括位置编码外推（RoPE、ALiBi）、Ring Attention 分布式训练，Gemini 1.5 Pro 已实现百万级 Token 上下文。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":331,"children":332},{},[333,334,341,342],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":335,"children":338},{"href":336,"rel":337},"https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.09849",[217],[339],{"type":192,"value":340},"Model Merging 论文",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":343,"children":346},{"href":344,"rel":345},"https://arxiv.org/abs/2312.00752",[217],[347],{"type":192,"value":348},"Long Context Survey",{"title":178,"searchDepth":350,"depth":350,"links":351},2,[352,353,354,355,356],{"id":197,"depth":350,"text":200},{"id":232,"depth":350,"text":235},{"id":270,"depth":350,"text":273},{"id":292,"depth":350,"text":295},{"id":322,"depth":350,"text":322},"markdown","content:6.maps:_ai:foundations:emerging.md","content","6.maps/_ai/foundations/emerging.md","6.maps/_ai/foundations/emerging","md",[364,368],{"_path":365,"title":366,"description":367},"/maps/_ai/foundations/core-concepts","AI Core Concepts","20个AI核心概念一句话速查",{"_path":369,"title":370,"description":371},"/maps/_ai/foundations/foundations","AI Foundations","Fundamental concepts, architectures, and industry dynamics in AI",1772504959118]